  "texts": [
    "In contrast to previous results, we observed significant misclassification.",
    "Internal content was often misclassified as external content (Fig. 7c, r =.29, p < 0.001) and external content was often misclassified as internal content (Fig.",
    "7d, r =.34, p < 0.001).",
    "Even though we found greater correct classification of internal content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.57 vs. R 2 = 0.08), misclassification rates were high.",
    "We also found greater correct classification of external content than misclassification (R 2 = 0.44.vs."
